# Root Lyfe Chess

Interactive chess board with:

- Standard 8x8 board
- Unicode pieces
- Click-to-select and move pieces
- Mobile-friendly
- Highlight for selected piece

**How to play:**  
Click/tap a piece, then click/tap a destination square. Currently allows basic moves; future upgrades can include legal move enforcement, turn tracking, and AI.

